00:06:51.430 --> 00:06:52.730
Fake news.

00:06:52.730 --> 00:06:54.370
Now, believe it or not,
there are people who think

00:06:54.370 --> 00:06:56.870
that fake news is not really
all that big of a problem.

00:06:56.870 --> 00:07:00.260
And there was a fair amount of
discussion earlier this year

00:07:00.260 --> 00:07:03.700
in journalism reviews and
journalism periodicals

00:07:03.700 --> 00:07:07.960 position:56%
