00:07:07.960 --> 00:07:11.650
The thinking was, "Well, fake
news is kind of ephemeral."

00:07:11.650 --> 00:07:15.050
It appears on these
way out there websites,

00:07:15.050 --> 00:07:18.180
and it's really not getting
all that many eyeballs compared

00:07:18.180 --> 00:07:21.550
to mainstream media outlets.

00:07:21.550 --> 00:07:24.060
Both traditional and online.

00:07:24.060 --> 00:07:27.970
So there's this thinking that
maybe we're overstating fake news,

00:07:27.970 --> 00:07:31.870 position:56%
