00:08:22.860 --> 00:08:26.400
It's not even close to being
plausible, but nonetheless it was

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:28.230
out there in these --

00:08:28.230 --> 00:08:32.140
the Netherland, the
netherworld of the internet.

00:08:32.140 --> 00:08:36.810
And this was an example of fake
news that really went viral.

00:08:36.810 --> 00:08:41.210
And this episode in which a
