even though it's been widely

00:09:01.330 --> 00:09:05.130
debunked, routinely
rejected as implausible.

00:09:05.130 --> 00:09:09.000
But it exists, and it's out there,
and it continues to circulate.

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:13.390
So it is an example of fake
news being a serious problem

00:09:13.390 --> 00:09:16.930
or turning into a serious problem.

00:09:16.930 --> 00:09:21.590
And then just the other day, just
