00:19:58.280 --> 00:19:59.580
Serious stuff.

00:19:59.580 --> 00:20:00.880
Serious stuff.

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:03.850
The Russians are tapping
in to the electrical grid.

00:20:03.850 --> 00:20:07.320
You know, there's potential
problems ahead.

00:20:07.320 --> 00:20:12.090
The story turned out to be
considerably less than that.

00:20:12.090 --> 00:20:17.130
There was one laptop at a Vermont
