00:24:26.140 --> 00:24:29.340 position:56%
In any event, it's not as good, I
guess, as "All the President's Men,"

00:24:29.340 --> 00:24:30.940
the movie version or
the cinematic version

00:24:30.940 --> 00:24:33.780
of "All the President's Men."

00:24:33.780 --> 00:24:40.220
It's interesting that even
at the "Post" the principles

00:24:40.220 --> 00:24:41.520
on the news side of the "Post"

00:24:41.520 --> 00:24:44.480
over the years have
rejected this interpretation,

00:24:44.480 --> 00:24:49.560
this heroic journalist
narrative of Watergate.

00:24:49.560 --> 00:24:52.590
They've scoffed at it.

00:24:52.590 --> 00:24:55.440
Katharine Graham who was the
publisher before, during,

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:59.790
