00:24:59.790 --> 00:25:02.840
of the break in, the seminal
crime of the Watergate scandal,

00:25:02.840 --> 00:25:07.040
a break in at Democratic National
Headquarters, in June of 1972.

00:25:07.040 --> 00:25:10.800
She said at the 25th anniversary of
this, "Sometimes people accuse us

00:25:10.800 --> 00:25:14.550
of bringing down a president,
which of course we did not do."

00:25:14.550 --> 00:25:17.720
The processes that caused
Richard Nixon's resignation

00:25:17.720 --> 00:25:19.630
were constitutional.

00:25:19.630 --> 00:25:20.930
And she's not alone.

00:25:20.930 --> 00:25:23.770
Ben Bradley, the executive
editor of the "Post" at the time,

00:25:23.770 --> 00:25:29.780
shown here on your right,
