on in the summer of '72 and the fall

00:46:37.720 --> 00:46:40.950
and so on, we wouldn't have
had congressional committees.

00:46:40.950 --> 00:46:44.640
We wouldn't have had
deeper investigation.

00:46:44.640 --> 00:46:48.410
