01:02:48.200 --> 01:02:52.140
in the next sentence
editorializing about gun rights,

01:02:52.140 --> 01:02:54.170 position:56%
but those two sentences [inaudible].

01:02:54.170 --> 01:02:56.120
&gt;&gt; Joseph Campbell: They
get mashed together,

01:02:56.120 --> 01:03:00.500
and then lesser known
people who made a comment,

01:03:00.500 --> 01:03:04.050
it sort of gets transferred
to the likes of Lincoln

01:03:04.050 --> 01:03:06.780
or Jefferson or Einstein.

01:03:06.780 --> 01:03:08.400
I mean they're out there.

01:03:08.400 --> 01:03:10.850
There are people who like,
